{"tid":1893672,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"意大利新冠肺炎確診病例突破100宗　口罩短缺索價100歐元一盒","createTime":"2020-02-23T12:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-23T12:02:06.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"fec53a8d0e1f4c28d14bc9e57139512b900d1884","tid":1893672,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-23T12:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200223/_2020022318081067541.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200223%2F_2020022318081067541.jpg&h=3636925d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n意大利米蘭口罩短缺。AP圖片<br />\n<br />\n意大利新冠肺炎疫情擴散，確診病例突破100宗，北部倫巴第大區確診感染人數增至89人。<br />\n<br />\n意大利民眾亦紛紛搶購口罩，惟該國在本月10日前仍在外銷口罩至中國，國內如今開始供不應求。有店家直指，10年的口罩庫存10日就被買光；一盒100個裝的口罩更被炒至100歐元，極為誇張。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，米蘭南部一家藥局表示，一個上午就賣光店內所有的口罩，仍不斷收到客戶詢問，藥局試圖訂貨，但很多廠商都反映已無庫存，只能隔天再試。<br />\n<br />\n有些藥局只剩下每盒100枚口罩的大包裝商品，但是售價要100歐元(折合約844港元)，讓排隊客人躊躇不知買不買。一位客人表示，她用不上這麼大量的口罩，可能購入後會再上網分售給其他人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1207598/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E7%97%85%E4%BE%8B%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4100%E5%AE%97-%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E7%9F%AD%E7%BC%BA%E7%B4%A2%E5%83%B9100%E6%AD%90%E5%85%83%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1207598%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2588%25A9%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BE%258B%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%25A0%25B4100%25E5%25AE%2597-%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E7%259F%25AD%25E7%25BC%25BA%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%2583%25B9100%25E6%25AD%2590%25E5%2585%2583%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%259B%2592&d=c0FEOXRBadflfKsXjMdAyk2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=25cfc297\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1207598%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B-%25E6%2584%258F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%2588%25A9%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E7%2597%2585%25E4%25BE%258B%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%25A0%25B4100%25E5%25AE%2597-%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E7%259F%25AD%25E7%25BC%25BA%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%2583%25B9100%25E6%25AD%2590%25E5%2585%2583%25E4%25B8%2580%25E7%259B%2592&h=bcd31cf4\" target=\"_blank\">https://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1207598/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%A7%E5%88%A9%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E7%97%85%E4%BE%8B%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4100%E5%AE%97-%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E7%9F%AD%E7%BC%BA%E7%B4%A2%E5%83%B9100%E6%AD%90%E5%85%83%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%92</a>"}]}